Package codedraw.events

Enum Class Key

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Key>
codedraw.events.Key
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Key>, Constable
public enum Key extends Enum<Key>
Represents various Keys. The number keys have the prefix N. The numpad keys have the NUMPAD prefix. If the key is not found or unknown the key value UNDEFINED will be used.
